                        classification marking. Drafted on May 21 by <persName corresp="#p_BHG_1">Barnes</persName>. Sent through <persName corresp="#p_RBH_1">Read</persName>, who did not initial the memorandum.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1980-05-27">May 27, 1980</date>
                    </dateline>
